	<li>Demonstrated leadership, initiative and resourcefulness in school, community or work experience</li>
	<li>Strong work ethic, ability to multi-task and teamwork orientation</li>
	<li>Dedication to building a career in financial services</li>
	<li>Minimum GPA of 3.0</li>
</ul>

